      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single F1717-prescribed load configuration (5° offset, compression-bending). While this represents the standard regulatory condition, only one test condition was evaluated; no variation in offset angle or loading rate was explored. Achieved level 2 (single well-characterized condition) rather than required level 3 (multiple conditions). This shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory context where F1717 prescribes a single standard condition."
